The '''Frenzied River Clan''' was a [[Witches of Dathomir|Dathomiri Witch]] clan village located near the [[Frenzied River]] on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. Their teachings were similar to the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order's]] in that they were geared toward the [[Light side of the Force/Legends|light side of the Force]].<ref name="CPL">''[[The Courtship of Princess Leia]]''</ref>

